                     <interp inst="t18660507-483-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="embezzlement"></interp> for embezzling and stealing 2<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 17<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., 11<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 10<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., and 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 11<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 9<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., the moneys of <persName id="t18660507-name-238" type="victimName">
